thread.title: New Zealand traveller
thread.title_full: CEWE Photoworld reviewed by New Zealand traveller

author: New Zealand traveller
title: New Zealand traveller
text:
Extraordinarily quick service but I would have prefered to design it all myself rather than adjust their designer's ideas. I had an enormous number of good photographs and would have slightly altered the ones I used if I could have seen what they would look like on the page.
But beautiful book and I will use them again
